==============
Version 2.18.0
==============

  Code name:

	* "Not enough love"

  Fixes:

	* Better localization (Theppitak Karoonboonyanan):
		http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=353236
		http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=402089

	* Temporary fix to work on distributions which don't have the
	  xdg.DesktopEntry module for Python (Federico Mena-Quintero):
		http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=397742

	* Be as lenient as we used to be while committing the changes
	  in a profile, instead of aborting immediately 
	  (Federico Mena-Quintero).

