Version 0.18
============

  Features

	+ Allow profiles to be downloaded using HTTP (DV)
	+ Allow the users database to be remote too (DV)
	+ Add a dialog for associating profiles with users (Mark)
	+ Re-work the layout of the profiles dialog (Mark)
	+ Support for Firefox bookmarks (John)
	+ Gentoo support (Joshua Hoblitt)

  Fixes

	+ Fix syntax error in sabayon-xinitrc.sh (Sebastien Bacher)
	+ Fix issue with saving profiles when /tmp and /etc are on
          different partitions (Sebastien Bacher)
	+ Fix hang when exiting the prototype session (Mark)
	+ Actually lookup to apply the profile from the users database (Mark)

